# {{REPO_NAME}} — domain glossary

Code, tests, and API fields use these words and no synonyms. A term absent from this file does
not exist in the codebase — add it here first.

This file is the reason two services can talk about the same noun without meaning different
things. Keep it short enough that people actually read it, and precise enough that a
disagreement about a word is settled here rather than in review.

## {{CONTEXT_NAME}} — `{{FIRST_PROJECT}}`

- **Term** — one-line definition. Say what it is, and where useful say what it is *not*: the
  exclusions are what stop the word drifting.

## Across contexts

Where the same word means different things in two projects, say so explicitly and say why
unifying them would be wrong. That note is worth more than either definition alone.
